      "node_id": "to_qubo",
      "parent_id": "mwis_SA_root",
      "name": "to_qubo",
      "description": "Convert a MISInstance to a qubo matrix.\n\nQUBO formulation:\nMinimize:\n    Q(x) = -∑_{i ∈ V} w_i x_i  +  λ ∑_{(i, j) ∈ E} x_i x_j\n\nArgs:\n    penalty (float, optional): Penalty factor. Defaults to None.\n\nRaises:\n    ValueError: When penalty is strictly inferior to 2 x max(weight).\n\nReturns:\n    np.ndarray: The QUBO matrix formulation of MIS.",
      "concept_type": "optimization",
      "inputs": [
        {
          "name": "graph",
          "type_desc": "Any",
          "constraints": "x is not None"
        },
        {
          "name": "penalty",
          "type_desc": "Any",
          "constraints": "x is not None"
        }
      ],
      "outputs": [
        {
          "name": "result",
          "type_desc": "np.ndarray",
          "constraints": "ndim >= 1"
        }
